User experience improvements
- Programme stability improvements and bug fixes.
Added some shortcuts for quick access to the [Edit] and [Convert] tabs in the PDF component.
- To quickly access the [Edit] tab, you can click [Edit PDF], [Add Text], or [Add Picture] in the Home tab.
- To quickly access the [Convert] tab, you can right-click on the document page and select [Convert to Word/Excel/PPT/Image]. You can also right-click on an image and select [Image to PDF] from the right-click menu.
